hostel.description:
Nitte provides In-campus Hostels for both boys and girls with 1689 capacity. Twin sharing rooms are available for 1st year students. Second year onwards boys may opt for twin sharing or four sharing rooms. The hostel mess operates on 'no-profit-no-loss' basis. Students are served both vegetarian and non-vegetarian food.
In-house wardens and the assistant wardens take care of the needs of students and help maintaining discipline in the hostel.

